org.fluidity.composition.spi.Dependency

    Package Description
    org.fluidity.composition.spi
    Service provider interfaces to handle special cases of software composition in Fluid Tools.

      <T> Dependency<T> ComponentFactory.Resolver.constant(T object)

      Calls ComponentFactory.Resolver.constructor(Class) on the given type, calls ComponentFactory.Resolver.resolve(Constructor) therewith, and returns the result.
